@node "Description" "Description"


 Description
 -----------

You select pattern, minimal size of file, source and destination drawer. And File extractor copy
corresponding files to destination drawer and if filenote is correct rename file to its real name.

It's usable when you want extract for example all jpeg larger than 10Kbytes from your IBrowse cache
and you want their real names not confusing 000012fe.jpg.
@endnode

