@node "Usage" "Usage"


 Usage
 -----

FileExtractor <pattern> <minsize> <sourcedirectory> <targetdirectory>

pattern - *.jpg, *.html, 0000*.*

minsize - minimal size of extracted file



for these parameters FileExtractor opens file requester

source directory - Ibrowse cache

destination directory - where you want copy selected files
@endnode

